#: ../../main_window/image_view.rst:233
msgid "Modifiers can be applied to every renaming option."
msgstr "Možnosti premenovania súborov"

#: ../../main_window/image_view.rst:235
msgid ""
"It is possible to assign multiple modifiers to an option - they are applied "
"in the order you assign them."
msgstr ""
"Je možné priradiť viacero modifikátorov k jednej možnosti – aplikujú sa v "
